[[Translation:en/Archive/Manual/Regional Investigator]]
A government official who investigates improper or unethical behavior in business and provides oversight of the [[en/Manual/Local authority|local authorities]]. If he catches a [[en/Manual/Transport company|transport company]] [[en/Manual/Local authority#pass-a-bribe|bribing a local authority]], he will block that companies services for that area for six months.

